title: DJ answers draft questions from media
itunes:title: DJ answers draft questions from media
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is back with a special new episode. DJ answers questions from the media through a conference call regarding the draft, combine, team fits and all the prospects within it. All things NFL draft are covered on the call!
